    <section id="overview">
      <h2>TD Pages &amp; Magick Link: Overview &amp; Pricing</h2>
      <p>The offer bundles two products from within the OLSP ecosystem, both created under Wayne Crowe's brand. The Magick Link is the affiliate link component; TD Pages is the page-builder software that helps members build the squeeze pages and landing pages those links need to convert traffic into opt-ins and clicks.</p>

      <h3>What's Included</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Magick Link ($7 one-time):</strong> a personal rotator affiliate link that cycles clicks through a library of curated OLSP offers. Owners earn a reported $0.30 per qualifying click and 100% commission ($7) on each new Magick Link resale. Also includes 100 free clicks as a bonus — see the pricing caution below for the conditions attached.</li>
        <li><strong>TD Pages (14-day free trial, then $47/month):</strong> a landing-page and squeeze-page builder with a library of pre-built, high-converting templates. Includes unlimited campaigns, monthly new template additions, 10,000 impressions per month on the entry plan, a 2-hour list-building training video, and access to "Traffic Nemesis" training content.</li>
        <li><strong>Earn-As-You-Learn training:</strong> step-by-step onboarding covering how to build a landing page in TD Pages, connect it to a recommended autoresponder, and drive the initial clicks through your Magick Link.</li>
        <li><strong>Live coaching sessions:</strong> access to recurring OLSP live sessions (reported as three per week — Tuesday, Thursday, Saturday) with Wayne Crowe covering traffic and list-building strategy.</li>
        <li><strong>OLSP community access:</strong> entry to the broader OLSP member community alongside users of other OLSP products including <a href="https://olsp.profitandprivilege.com/reviews/olsp-community-builders/">OLSP Community Builders</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Optional upsells:</strong> advanced roadmap training, AI tools, and a "live commission system" are described in marketing as optional paid upgrades beyond the core $7 entry.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Reported Pricing</h3>
      <div class="callout warn">
        <strong>Pricing and conditions caution:</strong> The $0.30-per-click earning applies only to traffic purchased from OLSP's own in-house solo ad provider — not organic social traffic or independently sourced paid traffic. The 100 free clicks bonus requires that you use TD Pages and OLSP's recommended autoresponder; using alternative tools disqualifies you from this bonus. TD Pages pricing found across public sources ranges from $47 to $97 per month depending on the plan tier, with a separate lifetime Pro option reported at $497. Treat all figures below as a general guide drawn from publicly available pages, not a confirmed current price list — verify directly on the official sales pages before purchasing anything.
      </div>
