      <p>TD Pages cites "conversion rates of up to 70%" in some marketing materials, which is at the high end of published squeeze-page benchmarks. The caveat language on the official page ("depends on a number of factors — every campaign is different") accurately reflects the reality that conversion rates are driven by traffic quality, offer alignment, and headline copy as much as by template design. No independently audited conversion data for TD Pages templates exists in publicly available sources.</p>

